features: Car Tissue Boxes: These cylinder tissues for car cup holder holders feature 4 marble designs with shimmering gold foil accents in the background and come in white, black, and pink
Versatile: The round tissue box set can be conveniently stored in your car cupholder, or take it on the go in your backpack, purse, or makeup kit; refill using the top opening

Absorbency at Your Fingertips: These tissues for car use are made of wooden pulp material that is highly absorbent so you can wipe your face, nose, or hands; each tube is crafted with 500gsm cardstock
Perfect Fit for Cup Holder: Each container measures 2.7 inches in diameter and 6.5 inches tall, perfectly sized to fit into any standard-size vehicle cup holder; each tissue measures 6.75x6 inches
Package Contents: The pack includes 8 cylinder cup holder tissues for car; each container tube has 50 tissues for a total of 400 tissues to keep in your bathroom, kitchen, or living room
body.description: Give your nose the gift of comfort with this 8-pack of portable cup holder tissue boxes. These tissue for car use are perfect for cleaning your nose and face but can also be used to clean your hands and some spills. The cylinder gold foil tissue boxes measure 2.7x6.5 inches and hold 50 tissues each. Place the round box in a vehicle cup holder, travel bag, or purse to be taken on the go, or use them for a nursery, café, or waiting room. The containers have 4 elegant designs with gold foil prints that are great for home or office decor. The cylindrical shape adds a touch of elegance to your decor and makes it easy to fit into any corner or small space. Made from high-quality materials, the cylinder tissue box is durable and long-lasting. Its sturdy construction ensures your tissues stay securely in place, helping to prevent them from falling out or getting crushed. The top of the box is open, making it easy to refill the tissues whenever necessary. This tissue box is also an excellent gift idea for friends and family. Its stylish design and practical functionality make it a thoughtful and useful present for any occasion, from a housewarming to birthdays.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2022
reviews.reviewText: They arent like the top tier quality of tissue but who really cares, it's a tissue and it gets the job done. theres a lot of individual tissues and it comes with a lot of packages, so i have found they are lasting a long enough time and are a good value. my main LOVE is the design. everyone needs tissues, so i just ordered this bc i think kleenex boxes throughout the house look so dumb but are necessary. these actually look sooo classy and chic. i kept the empty tissue cylinders when they run out because of how nice they look, they could definitely be reused for something! overall id say definitely get these if you need a lot of tissues and want them to look nice. only complaint is its not bottom heavy enough so you have to physically pick up the cylinder to grab a tissue (oh the horror). good price and good quality, would recommend
